<h2><strong>+ LIVE MUSIC </strong></h2>
</div>

<p>The event will be accompanied by soe live music, from the great duo from Cullercoats, The Creels, and from the Star and Shadow very own organ player, Carl Heslop!</p>
<p>The Creels are a pretty fabulous band, and you can listen to their music here (latest tunes at the bottom):</p>
